Prince Harry and Meghan Markle Recreate Their First Public Appearance Together at the Invictus Games|http://www.elle.com|http://www.elle.com/culture/a23976572/prince-harry-meghan-markle-recreate-appearance-invictus-games/||2018-10-20|Ariana Yaptangco||Meghan Markle and Prince Harry kicked off the 2018 Sydney Invictus Games in familiar fashion. As part of their Australian royal tour, the couple arrived to Day 1 of the sporting event hand-in-hand, making an adorable nod to their first public appearance together.

Just a year ago, Meghan made her public event debut with Harry at the Invictus Games in Toronto. Fast forward and the sight is super similar, with the now-married royals holding hands, wearing sunglasses, and looking totally in love.

